{"tid":1524121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推上聯合國，告上國際","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T18:40:01.000Z","uid":118941,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ccfafdb1cc4b8f35f8720eaf603284a61f3c011","tid":1524121,"uid":118941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/70284/%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%81%9A%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%EF%BC%9F%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F%E3%80%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F70284%2F%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25EF%25BC%259F%25E2%2594%2580%25E2%2594%2580%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F%25E3%2580%2581%2F&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70gjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=3ad5ff01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/70284/%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%81%9A%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%EF%BC%9F%E2%94%80%E2%94%80%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F%E3%80%81/</a><br />\n<br />\n羅沃啟表示，如果市民曾經被警察毆打，或遭受過任何不人道的對待，都可以聯絡聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處（Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights，簡稱OHCHR）。他舉例指，受害者可將驗傷報告、其他證據以及事發經過，以電郵或郵寄方式發送至OHCHR。雖然OHCHR未必有人手逐個個案去處理，但它會整體去進行調查及跟進。他又指，市民亦可將資料交給香港人權監察，他會親身去跟進。<br />\n<br />\n至於「文化監暴」表示或會就警察濫權告上國際刑事法庭，羅沃啟則認為個別人士自己去做的難度相當高，反而若聯合國有足夠資料時，可以代表香港人去國際刑事法庭訴訟；而且國際刑事法庭比較公平公正，不會顧慮中國的面子，「威力」不容忽視。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請各位今晚受傷既，之前受傷既，去相熟醫生驗傷。將驗傷報告send去聯合國，告上國際刑事法庭</span>"},{"pid":"efdce3f91840226029a9a222a1b828cf69062989","tid":1524121,"uid":308567,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"［文宣超新星爆炸］ 魔警阻止人道救援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMjHJNz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMjHJNz.jpg&h=3027d600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F125201912155933%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70gjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=89641699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚唔人道 係咪可以推到班撚樣上軍事法庭<br />\nSorry P牌每日一post 有冇手足幫手開post"},{"pid":"88456bb30fd589e3bd7c4911b09e053b5b09284d","tid":1524121,"uid":46314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"7b111d1a200db1dc3f215c53a8a7ff934539a255","tid":1524121,"uid":258788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"push, 告上國際"},{"pid":"bec191c439066092c3ded2438884201200e702c3","tid":1524121,"uid":118941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7e47b4b373110c609d8b2972ba16bc0e7d6a4164","tid":1524121,"uid":205638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7afa3a4e16cd0bf9c1474347a448d6844d169c93","tid":1524121,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70gjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=bf0def7d\" target=\"_blank\">