望大家幫幫手，識傷者既叫佢地揾相熟醫生驗傷，然後將報告send去聯合國ohchr，同時收集各種證據send埋過去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ohchr.org/EN/AboutUs/Pages/SocialMedia.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FEN%2FAboutUs%2FPages%2FSocialMedia.aspx&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70gjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=ad992178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ohchr.org/EN/AboutUs/Pages/SocialMedia.aspx</a>"}]}